name: i am Alis in Ordinarz Land
description: I am an Asian girl, I live somewhere like the end of the world, where life has no meaning and definition but my world is a world outside of here, my world is full of passion and color, in my world there is a sense of life and I am in  I move beyond my world, my dreams take me forward, time has no definition, I have the feeling of Alice being born in Wonderland but nothing strange, I see and grow the colors of life in a sea of gray, like a lotus  In the swamp
